1.11	Poolhall_Junkies	Poolhall Junkies	Poolhall Junkies is a 2002 drama/thriller film written, starring and directed by Mars Callahan. The film also stars Alison Eastwood, Michael Rosenbaum, Rick Schroder with Chazz Palminteri and Christopher Walken. It is the story of a pool hustler who is opposed by Joe (his former mentor) and Joe's new prodigy, in a climactic big-stakes nine-ball [[Glossary of cue sports terms#	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/54/Poolhall_Junkies.jpg/220px-Poolhall_Junkies.jpg
